item.title: Foxlike- Eclipse
item.dc:creator: calmor
item.description:
I actually really like it. Nice job man, you’ve got a killer arp <333

One thing tho, I do think that there’s a little too much going on in the middle, in terms of the different sound effects, such as the exhale, but other than that, it’s solid. Or, instead of “too much going on”, it could have had breaks in the song where the sound effects are to give it a dynamic feel to it, if you know what I mean. Anyway, awesome work
